                  <run fontcolor='#e15759' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='15' italic='true'>: Identifies the busiest blocks of the week. Darker squares indicate patient surges, allowing hospital staff schedulers to pinpoint exact days and hours where extra coverage is needed.</run>
